sentences: During 1989, she lived in London where she first came into contact with electronic music.

Due to problems with distribution, she gave the Braincandy label up in 1997 and instead began organizing parties with the name, "Pitch Control".
She released her first album, Stadtkind, in 2001, and her second album, Berlinette, in 2003.
